sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway / Istio<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant HTTP as vLLM HTTP API<br/>8000/TCP HTTP plaintext
    participant GRPC as vLLM TGIS Adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA
    participant S3 as S3 / PVC / HF Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Engine,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
    Engine->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Storage credentials / HF Token
    S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>GPU: Load model into GPU memory<br/>CUDA

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token / OAuth
    Gateway->>HTTP: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 plaintext (in-cluster)<br/>Auth delegated to KServe
    HTTP->>Engine: Inference request
    Engine->>GPU: CUDA compute<br/>(PagedAttention + continuous batching)
    GPU-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>HTTP: Generated text
    HTTP-->>Gateway: HTTP response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: gRPC/TGIS Inference Request
    Client->>GRPC: GenerationService RPC<br/>gRPC/8033 plaintext (in-cluster)
    GRPC->>Engine: Inference request
    Engine->>GPU: CUDA compute
    GPU-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>GRPC: Generated text
    GRPC-->>Client: gRPC response
